$ Oracle: Init parameter RECYCLEBIN
@ recyclebin

The value of the → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters[init parameter] `recyclebin` can be set to `on` or `off` which enables or disables the
→ development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables/recycle-bin.

If the value is set to `on`, dropping a table «moves» the table to the → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables/recycle-bin where they can be recovered again.

sa:

 `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/recyclebin`

  The SQL verb `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/verbs/purge`.

  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
